aegis-virus-scanner: Aegis is a virus scanner for Linux/Unix systems with
aegis-virus-scanner: a simple and intuitive user interface.
aegis-virus-scanner: 
aegis-virus-scanner: Aegis supports scanning of subdirectories, hidden files
aegis-virus-scanner: and .zip and .tar archive files, and drag-and-drop of
aegis-virus-scanner: files from the Nautilus file browser, or your Gnome
aegis-virus-scanner: desktop. When a virus is detected you can choose to
aegis-virus-scanner: delete, quarantine or rename the file.
